{
  "stem": "1603.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one day I would look out on the window, and I will see all these bombs are falling into the Danube River but like raining, like training.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you can imagine that was thousands of bombs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if any bomb would have fallen on the streetcar, which was lined up before our house, the whole neighborhood would have disappeared.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was another interesting experience in-- in our lives when the landlady where we stayed in her apartment, said, well, I can't take this any longer, because the law was in Hungary if you were hiding Jews, and the Germans were catching you-- that you're hiding Jews, you were executed with the Jews immediately on the street.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she had kids also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she said we have to leave immediately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, she had just a nervous breakdown, and we understood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She helped us a lot, and she was very nice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So immediately we had to go and walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Luckily, five or six miles away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Uh, there was another apartment, some friends who moved out from it and also escaped from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the apartment became empty, and we heard about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were able to go and walk towards that place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that was before Christmas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we walked out from this apartment building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't know, it took us a very long time, because the air raids were so strong that many times we had to throw our bodies on the-- on the-- on the street, down, because we were thinking that we're going to get killed.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to cross a bridge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
